375	//
376	// `inlineOracle` is a TEST-LOCAL reproduction of the exact algorithm the old
377	// `admin/content.tsx` action ran for the save/publish intent (verified against
378	// `feature/registration-launch:app/routes/admin/content.tsx`):
379	//   base = encodeDocument(current)
380	//   merged = deepMerge(deepMerge(base, assembleOverrides(entries)),
381	//                      { translations: collectTranslations(entries) })
382	//   decoded = decodeDocument(merged)
383	//   stored  = encodeDocumentJson(decoded)
384	// The corpus asserts `DraftEditor.editDocument(scope, routeOverride(entries))`
385	// produces a draft byte-identical to the oracle's `stored` JSON across every
386	// override shape the route's two override-builders emit: dotted-path leaves,
387	// translation fields (`t:<locale>:<key>` → `collectTranslations`), numeric
388	// coercions (bible.chapter/verse), nested hero keys, team fields, and the
389	// preserved-unedited `registration` Option deep-field survival.
